res need to be able to integrate into a team and work well in the company environment- after all, reading candidate\'s drive is part of HR\'s skill. So how can they work together seamless?<\\/p><p>Moreover, miscommunication, delayed updating interview schedules always slow down the process. The interview room always the first place an interviewer see an candidates\' resume. Then how can they make the professional skill based judgement in 20 mins?<\\/p>\",\"19\":\"Project Brief\",\"10\":\"\",\"11\":\"\",\"58\":\"blue\",\"25\":{\"265\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"An Embarrassing Conversation\",\"body\":\"<p><strong>Front Desk Lady: <\\/strong>Hey Joe, your interviewee is waiting for you, are you ready?<\\/p><p><strong>Joe: <\\/strong>An interviewee? Never heard about it. Are we hiring?<\\/p><p><strong>IT WON\'T BE FUNNY IF WE KEEP RUNNING INTO THIS..<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"264\"],\"layout\":\"fluid\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"263\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Personas\",\"body\":\"<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"260\",\"261\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"267\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Ideations\",\"body\":\"<ul><li>Intuitive candidate based tracking flow and manageable pipeline.<\\/li><li>Administrator login and visitor login funnel. Team tools for sharing, scheduling and feedback collection.<\\/li><li>Seamless integrate with Gmail, Outlook and Calendar.<\\/li><li>Automatic resume parser but also accessible to original files.<\\/li><li>Recruiting intelligence, highlight candidates in keywords and descriptions.<\\/li><li>Scientific rating and weighting system help you avoid bias.<\\/li><li>Powerful search and filter function available.<\\/li><li>Connect with mainstream job posting platforms (Linkedin, Monster).<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"media\":[\"266\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"270\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"User Flow\",\"body\":\"<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"269\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"274\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Interviewer\\r\\nUser Flow\",\"body\":\"<p>Sign in -&gt; ( Review Profile ) -&gt; Give comments\\/ feedback\\/rate |  Change Interview time. <\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"273\",\"272\",\"271\",\"276\",\"275\"],\"layout\":\"fluid\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"281\":{\"type\":\"comparisonFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Reschedule\\r\\nInterview\",\"body\":\"<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.<\\/p>\",\"images\":[\"279\",\"280\"],\"firstCaption\":\"Success State\",\"secondCaption\":\"Failed State\",\"fadeEnabled\":\"\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"HR Recruiter\\r\\nUser Flow\",\"body\":\"<p>Sign in -&gt; (Add a new position) -&gt; (Add new candidates) -&gt; Set up interview time |  Change Interview time-&gt; Conduct HR interview and update comments | Provide offers| Manage Candidate bank and more.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"289\",\"285\",